      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，入侵检测作为起点。加密环节您说的是一个步骤还是两个？我看您提到了两次加密。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是两个独立的加密层，第一层是传输加密，第二层是存储加密，这样更严谨。所以入侵检测之后要连两个加密节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Encryption",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把入侵检测放在最左边，然后接两个加密节点，方向从左到右。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "加密之后需要防火墙，而且防火墙也要分两层，一层是网络边界防火墙，一层是应用层防火墙，最后那个节点就是终点了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_Firewall"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，流程是：入侵检测 → 传输加密 → 存储加密 → 网络防火墙 → 应用防火墙，总共五个节点，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，就是这个顺序。每个节点用方框，标注清楚功能。",
